<paragraph id="8BFF36A9FF90CE254E9D53FCAFD1AB13" blockId="33.[151,1437,939,1025]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis id="B934EABBFF90CE254E9D53FCAD69ACD1" bold="true" box="[151,271,939,963]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Synonyms:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C404D2AFF90CE254F1253FBAF7CACD1" authority="Melika &amp; Abrahamson, 2007" authorityName="Melika &amp; Abrahamson" authorityYear="2007" box="[280,794,939,963]" class="Insecta" family="Cynipidae" genus="Bassettia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="archboldi" status="syn. nov.">
<emphasis id="B934EABBFF90CE254F1253FBAD86ACD1" box="[280,480,939,963]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Bassettia archboldi</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFD14B58FF90CE254FE253FCAF7CACD1" author="Melika, G. &amp; Abrahamson, W. G." box="[488,794,939,963]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" pagination="131 - 148" refId="ref41617" refString="Melika, G. &amp; Abrahamson, W. G. (2007) Review of the Nearctic gall wasp species of the genus Bassettia Ashmead, 1887, with description of new species (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae, 53 (2), 131 - 148." type="journal article" year="2007">Melika &amp; Abrahamson, 2007</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<emphasis id="B934EABBFF90CE254D2D53FCAFE1ACD1" bold="true" box="[807,903,939,963]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A20757C0FF90CE254D2D53FCAFE1ACD1" box="[807,903,939,963]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">syn. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
This species was initially described based only on males, without knowledge of the females or the galls they induce; a male was obtained in a Malaise trap in November in 
<collectingRegion id="4984F84BFF90CE254ECD53BFAD75AB12" box="[199,275,1000,1024]" country="United States of America" name="Florida" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Florida</collectingRegion>
, at the Archbold Biological Station (
<bibRefCitation id="EFD14B58FF90CE254C8E53BFAFCDAB13" author="Melika, G. &amp; Abrahamson, W. G." box="[644,939,1000,1025]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34" pagination="131 - 148" refId="ref41617" refString="Melika, G. &amp; Abrahamson, W. G. (2007) Review of the Nearctic gall wasp species of the genus Bassettia Ashmead, 1887, with description of new species (Hymenoptera: Cynipidae: Cynipini). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae, 53 (2), 131 - 148." type="journal article" year="2007">Melika &amp; Abrahamson 2007</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
